title: [Teorainn Valley, Brambles]
description: The thick mass of brambles stands tall along both sides of the stony path.  The air is still and fusty.  Motes of dust hang in the air, illuminated by the moonlight.  The long, sharp spikes of the brambles loom menacingly.
